ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.group5

Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.group5.Location

  • public class Location
extends java.lang.Object
    Takes a cityId then fetches the current weather, forecast by day and forecast by 3-hour increments from the OWM server in JSON format. The JSON string is then parsed and the pertinent data is stored in one object of CurrentWeather, 5 objects of LongTerm (ie 5 days daily forecast) and 8 objects of ShortTerm (ie 8*3 = 24 hour forecast).
    Author:
    CS2212 Team 5
